name: table.public.country
description: Holds a list of Countries which we support

sync.name: input
sync.source:
SELECT etag,
 fields ->> 'id'::text AS id,
 fields ->> 'Title'::text AS title,
   fields ->> 'Flag'::text AS flag
 FROM sync.sharepoint_items('%cava3%'::text) sharepoint_items(id, etag, fields, listname)
 WHERE listname = 'Countries'::text;
